# Butter

Use Butter for UI, frontend, component, Tailwind, React, shadcn, and visual design tasks.

Core directive: make touched UI visibly better. Improve animation, animated text/numbers, hierarchy, spacing, and state transitions. Do not leave static generic UI.

Read canonical files before implementation:
- `skills/SKILL.md`
- `skills/visual/SKILL.md`
- `skills/motion/SKILL.md`
- `skills/patterns/SKILL.md`
- `skills/construction/SKILL.md`

Preserve Butter feel: compact object UI, neutral shell, stateful accent, `24-40px` expressive radius, `44-56px` controls, tabular numerals, semibold/bold labels, tactile springs, animated text/number bloom, linear progress, no decorative blobs or generic gradients.
